data.description: GEM IN SHARONDALE!  Located in beautiful, desirable senior community of Sharondale.  Situated on Cul-de-sac, this home features 2 suites and 3 bathrooms. This is one the larger units in Shardondale,  boasting 1,980 sq.ft. PRIVACY AND SERENITY with open space behind the property.  Greenbelt and trees located in rear of property.  2 car garage.  Open floor plan with living room open to dining area.  House in need of repairs. Large Separate laundry room for office combo or lots of storage.  Master bath features dual sinks, separate shower and large soaking tub.  PERMANENT foundation.  Mature landscaping providing that desired tranquility and plenty of area to enjoy with family and friends.  HOA amenities include saltwater pool/spa, club house, billiard room, cardroom , meeting room, exercise area, enjoyment of greenbelts throughout community, metered water and sewer included.  MUST SEE!!
